org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabMergeRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabMergeRequest

  • public final class GitlabMergeRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Merge Request. To create, update, or delete this issue, call create(), update(), or delete() explicitly. This supports query for merge requests globally or within a GitlabProject. See GitlabMergeRequest.Query and GitlabMergeRequest.ProjectQuery respectively. Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/merge_requests.html

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  GitlabMergeRequest.ProjectQuery
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query merge requests within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
      static class  GitlabMergeRequest.Query
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global GitlabMergeRequests with searching scope and range.
